Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.33,0:22:56.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.12,0:23:00.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然假声有些失败
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.80,0:23:03.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.01,0:23:04.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很感动
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.10,0:23:05.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.22,0:23:05.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很感动
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.08,0:23:06.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.36,0:23:06.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很感动
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.07,0:23:07.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.61,0:23:13.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  下集的幸运星是？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.82,0:23:14.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是日和
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.41,0:23:15.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是帕多里西亚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.52,0:23:16.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕蒂  已经适应打工了？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.97,0:23:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没问题的说
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.23,0:23:19.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是帕蒂来招待的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.28,0:23:22.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是第一次到店里来的客人也能毫不紧张地享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.85,0:23:25.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我是不会接待第一次来的客人的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.47,0:23:26.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.49,0:23:30.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是来了很多次  消费很多的客人的话  是不提供服务的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.11,0:23:32.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是店里的方针
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.77,0:23:34.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意…意外的很严格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.97,0:23:35.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.71,0:23:36.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「二次元里体现着本质」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.06,0:23:38.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬请期待
